<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>337</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Paucham phat deihum ahi, Lunggil kingainiem a,
 Hukdampa leh guol, Isu kawma kikhawm in;
 Ginna tawh a kawm zuon leng, A venna chang dingin,
 Hatlo di'n hatna ahi, Aw anuom na ding e!

[V2]
 Paucham phat.... deihum.........!
 Paucham phat .... deihum .......!
 Hatlo di'n hatna ahi,
 Aw a nuomna ding e!

[V3]
 2. Paucham phat deih um ahi, Hukdampa a naih tieng,
 Lungsietna zainem tawh, A mite ngaitha di'n;
 I lungkham nau cheng, A kengbula tun di'n ei hilh,
 Hatlo di'n hatna ahi, Aw a nuom na ding e.

[V4]
 3. Paucham phat deihum ahi, thepna chetna thuokten,
 Lungkhamna amau hehpih, Tanpa hilh untin;
 A lungsietna lunggil in, buoina cheng lamang ding,
 Hatlo din hatna ahi, Aw a nuom na ding e!

[V5]
 4. Paucham phat deihum ahin, dettak a I gin chun,
 Vangpiekna I nget u chuh mungei ngei hitiu;
 Kipahna bukim neiin I buoinau cheng bei ding,
 Hatlo di'n hatna ahi, Aw a nuom na ding e!</lyrics>
<title>'TIS THE BLESSED HOUR OF PRAYER</title>
</song>